OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1783973917
OL,3,CSark wildfire 'under control' but
OL,4,Cfirefighters monitoring area for
OL,5,Cseveral days
OL,7,FFirefighters are expected to monitor
OL,8,Fthe site of a major wildfire in Sark
OL,9,Ffor 'at least several days'.
OL,11,FSark Fire and Rescue Service say the
OL,12,Ffire is now under control and that
OL,13,Fcrew members are continuing to dampen
OL,14,Fdown the headland on Little Sark, a
OL,15,Fday after the island's first major
OL,16,Fincident was declared.
OL,18,FExcavators have also been cutting fire
OL,19,Fbreaks through the gorse which was
OL,20,Fablaze.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1783973917
OL,3,CSark wildfire 'under control' but
OL,4,Cfirefighters monitoring area for
OL,5,Cseveral days
OL,7,FThe service also confirmed that no
OL,8,Fhomes have been damaged.
OL,10,FIn a statement, Kevin Adams, Chief
OL,11,FFire Officer for Sark Fire and Rescue
OL,12,FService, said: "The fire in little
OL,13,FSark has been a herculean effort from
OL,14,Feveryone involved. The 999 call came
OL,15,Fthrough at 11am Friday morning and,
OL,16,Falthough the fire is now under
OL,17,Fcontrol, firefighters are continuing
OL,18,Fto dampen down the area.
OL,20,F"It is expected that this will need to
OL,21,Fcontinue for at least several days.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1783973917
OL,3,CSark wildfire 'under control' but
OL,4,Cfirefighters monitoring area for
OL,5,Cseveral days
OL,7,FMr Adams added: "A field approximately
OL,8,Fsize of a football pitch was scorched
OL,9,Fover in approximately one minute. We
OL,10,Fmanaged to stop the flames from
OL,11,Freaching two private dwellings.
OL,12,FExcavators have been involved by
OL,13,Fcutting fire breaks through the gorse.
OL,15,F"Once again my thanks goes to everyone
OL,16,Finvolved from Guernsey Fire & Rescue,
OL,17,FGuernsey Harbour Office, JESCC,
OL,18,FGuernsey drone crew, Sarnia work boat,
OL,19,FSark Shipping, Sark charter vessels,
OL,20,FGuernsey Ambulance and Rescue and
OL,21,FFlying Christine III.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1783973917
OL,3,CSark wildfire 'under control' but
OL,4,Cfirefighters monitoring area for
OL,5,Cseveral days
OL,7,F"My thanks also goes to the too
OL,8,Fnumerous to count volunteers from
OL,9,FSark, including those who supplied the
OL,10,Ffire crews with food and water. At one
OL,11,Fpoint yesterday afternoon there was 50
OL,12,Fplus personnel assisting."
OL,14,FSark Police added that the incident
OL,15,Fwas 'extremely difficult' and
OL,16,F'worrying' for islanders.
OL,18,FThe force said: "This was a powerful
OL,19,Freminder of the strength, compassion
OL,20,Fand resilience that exists across our
OL,21,Fisland.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
