OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1783973917
OL,3,CSark wildfire 'under control' but
OL,4,Cfirefighters monitoring area for
OL,5,Cseveral days
OL,7,F"We are incredibly grateful to
OL,8,Feveryone who played a part in
OL,9,Fsupporting those affected and helping
OL,10,Four emergency services.
OL,12,F"Thank you all for pulling together
OL,13,Fwhen it mattered most."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
